{"prompt": "Build a modern website for a digital marketing agency. The design should prominently display a bold orange.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Digital Marketing Agency</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #FF7F50; /* Bold Orange */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #FF7F50; /* Bold Orange */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border: 1px solid #eee;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY